      "description": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "Explore past Kuala Lumpur's major attractions and discover illusion 3D Art Museum! Spend a day inside the museum, where gigantic 3D art paintings dominate the walls and the floors. Take photos of your friends and family posing in different kinds of scenarios; encounters with zombies and celebrities, dangerous cliffs and deadly accidents, as well as meetings with exotic animals. Get close to all 38 hand-painted pieces and enjoy them for as long as you want. Once your camera's storage capacity fills up, head next to the museum's Augmented Reality video studio. Step inside a world far away from reality as you interact with a real-time virtual environment of your choice. Pet an elephant by the riverbanks, meet extinct dinosaurs, or be stranded with a hungry polar bear in the middle of the ocean. Whatever you choose, you'll surely enjoy watching yourself after you're done."
          }
        ]
      },
